headline: Aurora to Host Second Quarter 2025 Business Review Conference Call on July 30, 2025
summary: PITTSBURGH, July 09, 2025--Aurora Innovation, Inc. (NASDAQ: AUR) today announced it will release second quarter 2025 results after market close on July 30, 2025 and will host a business review conference call that day at 5:00 p.m. Eastern time. The conference call will be webcast on Aurora’s investor relations website at ir.aurora.tech. A replay of the webcast will be available for 30 days following the call.
